section Section1;
shared Service_CRM = let
  Source = Oracle.Database("COHREP", [HierarchicalNavigation=true, Query="
SELECT
    sysdate                                                       extract_date,
    from_tz(CAST(sysdate AS TIMESTAMP), 'PST') AT TIME ZONE '"&Local&"'         local_extract_date,
    al2.incident_number,
    al2.operating_unit,
    al2.incident_type,
    nvl(al2.alternate_customer_name, al2.customer_name),
    al2.incident_severity,
    al2.incident_status,
    al2.escalation,
    al2.incident_owner,
    al2.incident_group_name,
    al7.inventory_item_id,
    al2.item_number,
    al2.item_description,
    al1.task_number,
    al2.serial_number,
    al1.task_type,
    al2.problem_code,
    al1.task_status,
    al1.owner,
    nvl(al2.technical_business_unit, 'Not Entered')               tbu,
    al1.actual_start_date,
    al1.actual_end_date,
    al2.incident_close_date,
    al2.regional_location,
    al2.incident_date,
    al2.entitlement,
    al2.inc_reported_date,
    nvl(al2.product_family, 'Not Entered')                        product_family,
    al7.install_date,
    MIN(al8.new_install_date)                                     original_install_date,
    al9.header_id,
    MAX(al10.line_id)                                             last_order_line_id,
    al10.order_status,
    al10.header_creation_date,
    al10.order_number,
    'Oracle CRM'                                                  system_source,
    decode(nvl(al2.obq_flag, 'N'), 'Y', 'Yes', 'No')              obq_flag,
    al2.obq_type,
    al2.obq_notes,
    al2.incident_instance,
    al10.warehouse
FROM
    apps.xxcoh_sr_tasks_view             al1,
    apps.xxcoh_service_request_view      al2,
    apps.csi_installed_base_v            al7,
    csi.csi_item_instances_h             al8,
    apps.xxcoh_sr_om_link_v              al9,
    appsread.xxcoh_service_order_view    al10,
    (
        SELECT
            msi.inventory_item_id
        FROM
            apps.mtl_system_items    msi,
            apps.mtl_parameters      mp
        WHERE
                mp.organization_id = msi.organization_id
            AND mp.organization_code = '"&ORG&"'
    ) msiv
WHERE
        al2.incident_id = al1.incident_id (+)
    AND al2.incident_instance = al7.instance_number (+)
    AND al7.instance_id = al8.instance_id (+)
    AND al2.incident_id = al9.incident_id (+)
    AND al9.header_id = al10.header_id (+)
    AND msiv.inventory_item_id = al7.inventory_item_id
    AND al2.incident_status NOT IN (
        'Cancelled',
        'Cancelled by User'
    )
    AND al8.old_install_date (+) IS NULL
    AND ( NOT al8.new_install_date (+) IS NULL )
    AND al1.task_type (+) LIKE 'Visit%'
    AND al2.incident_type IN (
        'Advance Replacement',
        'Depot Repair',
        'Field Service Visit',
        'LSM Depot Repair/Calibration',
        'Parts Order',
        'Return Replacement',
        'Upgrade'
    )
    AND ( NOT al1.task_status (+) = 'Cancelled' )
    AND al2.entitlement = 'Warranty'
GROUP BY
    al2.incident_number,
    al2.operating_unit,
    al2.incident_type,
    nvl(al2.alternate_customer_name, al2.customer_name),
    al2.incident_severity,
    al2.incident_status,
    al2.escalation,
    al2.incident_owner,
    al2.incident_group_name,
    al7.inventory_item_id,
    al2.item_number,
    al2.item_description,
    al1.task_number,
    al2.serial_number,
    al1.task_type,
    al2.problem_code,
    al1.task_status,
    al1.owner,
    nvl(al2.technical_business_unit, 'Not Entered'),
    al1.actual_start_date,
    al1.actual_end_date,
    al2.incident_close_date,
    al2.regional_location,
    al2.incident_date,
    al2.entitlement,
    al2.inc_reported_date,
    nvl(al2.product_family, 'Not Entered'),
    al7.install_date,
    al9.header_id,
    al10.order_status,
    al10.header_creation_date,
    al10.order_number,
    'Oracle CRM',
    sysdate,
    decode(nvl(al2.obq_flag, 'N'), 'Y', 'Yes', 'No'),
    al2.obq_type,
    al2.obq_notes,
    al2.incident_instance,
    AL10.WAREHOUSE
", CommandTimeout=#duration(0, 0, 10, 0)]),
  #"Renamed columns" = Table.RenameColumns(Source, {{"EXTRACT_DATE", "Extract Date"}, {"INCIDENT_NUMBER", "Incident Number"}, {"OPERATING_UNIT", "Operating Unit"}, {"INCIDENT_TYPE", "Incident Type"}, {"NVL(AL2.ALTERNATE_CUSTOMER_NAME,AL2.CUSTOMER_NAME)", "Customer Name"}, {"INCIDENT_SEVERITY", "Incident Severity"}, {"INCIDENT_STATUS", "Incident Status"}, {"ESCALATION", "Escalation"}, {"INCIDENT_OWNER", "Incident Owner"}, {"INCIDENT_GROUP_NAME", "Incident Group Name"}, {"ITEM_NUMBER", "Item Number"}, {"ITEM_DESCRIPTION", "Item Description"}, {"TASK_NUMBER", "Task Number"}, {"SERIAL_NUMBER", "Serial Number"}, {"TASK_TYPE", "Task Type"}, {"PROBLEM_CODE", "Problem Code"}, {"TASK_STATUS", "Task Status"}, {"OWNER", "Owner"}, {"ACTUAL_START_DATE", "Actual Start Date"}, {"ACTUAL_END_DATE", "Actual End Date"}, {"INCIDENT_CLOSE_DATE", "Incident Closed Date"}, {"REGIONAL_LOCATION", "Regional Location"}, {"INCIDENT_DATE", "Incident Date"}, {"ENTITLEMENT", "Entitlement"}, {"INC_REPORTED_DATE", "Incident Reported Date"}, {"PRODUCT_FAMILY", "Product Family"}, {"INSTALL_DATE", "Install Date"}, {"ORIGINAL_INSTALL_DATE", "Original Install Date"}, {"ORDER_STATUS", "Order Status"}, {"HEADER_CREATION_DATE", "Header Creation Date"}, {"OBQ_FLAG", "OBQ Flag"}, {"ORDER_NUMBER", "Order Number"}, {"SYSTEM_SOURCE", "System Source"}, {"OBQ_TYPE", "OBQ Type"}, {"OBQ_NOTES", "OBQ Notes"}, {"INCIDENT_INSTANCE", "Incident Instance"}, {"WAREHOUSE", "ORG"}, {"LOCAL_EXTRACT_DATE", "Local Extract Date"}})
in
  #"Renamed columns";
shared Service_Cloud = let
  Source = Oracle.Database("COHREP", [HierarchicalNavigation=true, Query="
SELECT
    sysdate                                                     extract_date,
    from_tz(CAST(sysdate AS TIMESTAMP), 'PST') AT TIME ZONE '"&Local&"'         local_extract_date,
    al12.casenumber                                             incident_number,
    al12.operating_unit_c                                       operating_unit,
    al12.c_type                                                 incident_type,
    al12.account                                                customer_name,
    al12.equipment_status_c                                     equipment_status,
    al12.c_status                                               incident_status,
    al12.isescalated                                            escalation,
    al12.c_owner                                                incident_owner,
    al12.service_groups_c                                       incident_group_name,
    (
        SELECT
            inventory_item_id
        FROM
            apps.mtl_system_items_b msi
        WHERE
                msi.segment1 = al12.part_number_c
            AND msi.organization_id = 63
    ) inventory_item_id,
    al12.part_number_c                                          item_number,
    al12.part_descr                                             item_description,
    al12.workordernumber                                        task_number,
    al12.serialnumber                                           serial_number,
    al12.wo_type                                                task_type,
    al12.case_reason_code_c                                     problem_code,
    al12.wo_status                                              task_status,
    al12.wo_owner                                               owner,
    al12.tbu_c                                                  tbu,
    al13.sa_actualstarttime                                     actual_start_date,
    al13.sa_actualendtime                                       actual_end_date,
    al12.closeddate                                             incident_closed_date,
    al12.region_location_c                                      regional_location,
    al12.createddate                                            incident_date,
    al12.billing_type_c                                         entitlement,
    al12.createddate2                                           incident_reported_date,
    al12.product_family_c                                       product_family,
    al12.installdate                                            install_date,
    al12.tmp_original_in33,
    xxsov.header_id,
    al14.ora_so_line_id_c                                       last_order_line_id,
    xxsov.order_status,
    xxsov.header_creation_date,
    xxsov.order_number,
    'Service Cloud CRM'                                         system_source,
    decode(nvl(al15.obq_c, 'N'), 'Y', 'Yes', 'No')                  obq_flag,
    al15.obq_type_c                                             obq_type,
    al15.obq_notes_c                                            obq_notes,
    al12.ora_ib_instance37                                      incident_instance,
    XXSOV.WAREHOUSE
FROM
    appsread.xxcoh_service_order_view xxsov,
    (
        SELECT
            d11al3.casenumber                                                                           AS casenumber,
            substr(d11al3.operating_unit_c, 1, instr(d11al3.operating_unit_c, ':') - 1)                      AS operating_unit_c,
            d11al3.type                                                                                 AS c_type,
            d11al1.name                                                                                 AS account,
            d11al3.equipment_status_c                                                                   AS equipment_status_c,
            d11al3.status                                                                               AS c_status,
            decode(d11al3.isescalated, 'false', 'Never Escalated', 'true', 'CARE Escalation')         AS isescalated,
            nvl(d11al9.name, d11al5.name)                                                              AS c_owner,
            d11al3.service_groups_c                                                                     AS service_groups_c,
            d11al6.part_number_c                                                                        AS part_number_c,
            d11al6.name                                                                                 AS part_descr,
            d11al7.workordernumber                                                                      AS workordernumber,
            d11al4.serialnumber                                                                         AS serialnumber,
            d11al8.name                                                                                 AS wo_type,
            d11al3.case_reason_code_c                                                                   AS case_reason_code_c,
            d11al7.status                                                                               AS wo_status,
            nvl(d11al11.name, d11al10.name)                                                            AS wo_owner,
            nvl(d11al6.tbu_c, 'Not Entered')                                                           AS tbu_c,
            d11al3.closeddate                                                                           AS closeddate,
            d11al3.region_location_c                                                                    AS region_location_c,
            d11al3.createddate                                                                          AS createddate,
            d11al3.billing_type_c                                                                       AS billing_type_c,
            d11al3.createddate                                                                          AS createddate2,
            nvl(d11al6.coherent_product_family_c, 'Not Entered')                                       AS product_family_c,
            d11al4.installdate                                                                          AS installdate,
            d11al4.installdate                                                                          AS tmp_original_in33,
            d11al3.id                                                                                   AS case_id,
            d11al4.ora_ib_instance_id_c * 1.0                                                           AS ora_ib_instance35,
            d11al7.id                                                                                   AS wo_id,
            d11al2.ora_ib_instance_id_c                                                                 AS ora_ib_instance37
        FROM
            sfdc.account       d11al1,
            sfdc.asset         d11al2,
            sfdc.case          d11al3,
            sfdc.asset         d11al4,
            sfdc.group_sfdc    d11al5,
            sfdc.product2      d11al6,
            sfdc.workorder     d11al7,
            sfdc.worktype      d11al8,
            sfdc.user_sfdc     d11al9,
            sfdc.group_sfdc    d11al10,
            sfdc.user_sfdc     d11al11
        WHERE
                d11al3.accountid = d11al1.id (+)
            AND d11al3.ownerid = d11al5.id (+)
            AND d11al3.ownerid = d11al9.id (+)
            AND d11al3.assetid = d11al2.id (+)
            AND d11al2.rootassetid = d11al4.id (+)
            AND d11al4.product2id = d11al6.id (+)
            AND d11al3.id = d11al7.caseid (+)
            AND d11al7.worktypeid = d11al8.id (+)
            AND d11al7.ownerid = d11al10.id (+)
            AND d11al7.ownerid = d11al11.id (+)
            AND d11al3.isdeleted = 'false'
            AND d11al3.status NOT IN (
                'Canceled',
                'Closed as Duplicate'
            )
            AND d11al7.isdeleted (+) = 'false'
            AND ( NOT d11al7.status (+) = 'Canceled' )
            AND d11al3.billing_type_c = 'Warranty'
    ) al12,
    (
        SELECT
            d12al1.casenumber                   AS casenumber,
            d12al1.type                         AS c_type,
            d12al1.status                       AS c_status,
            d12al2.workordernumber              AS workordernumber,
            d12al3.name                         AS wo_type,
            MAX(d12al4.appointmentnumber)      AS appointmentnumber,
            d12al4.actualstarttime              AS sa_actualstarttime,
            d12al4.actualendtime                AS sa_actualendtime,
            d12al1.id                           AS case_id,
            d12al2.id                           AS wo_id,
            d12al4.id                           AS sa_id
        FROM
            sfdc.case                  d12al1,
            sfdc.workorder             d12al2,
            sfdc.worktype              d12al3,
            sfdc.serviceappointment    d12al4
        WHERE
                d12al2.worktypeid = d12al3.id (+)
            AND d12al1.id = d12al2.caseid
            AND d12al2.id = d12al4.parentrecordid
            AND d12al4.isdeleted = 'false'
            AND d12al4.status NOT IN (
                'Canceled',
                'None'
            )
        GROUP BY
            d12al1.casenumber,
            d12al1.type,
            d12al1.status,
            d12al2.workordernumber,
            d12al3.name,
            d12al4.actualstarttime,
            d12al4.actualendtime,
            d12al1.id,
            d12al2.id,
            d12al4.id
    ) al13,
    (
        SELECT
            d13al1.casenumber                          AS casenumber,
            d13al1.type                                AS c_type,
            d13al3.workordernumber                     AS workordernumber,
            d13al2.ora_so_header_id_c                  AS ora_so_header_id_c,
            MAX(d13al2.ora_so_line_id_c) * 1.0        AS ora_so_line_id_c,
            d13al2.billing_type_c                      AS billing_type_c,
            d13al1.id                                  AS case_id,
            d13al3.id                                  AS wo_id
        FROM
            sfdc.case                 d13al1,
            sfdc.workorderlineitem    d13al2,
            sfdc.workorder            d13al3
        WHERE
                d13al1.id = d13al3.caseid
            AND d13al2.workorderid = d13al3.id
            AND d13al2.order_classification_c = 'External Order'
            AND d13al2.ora_so_header_id_c IS NOT NULL
        GROUP BY
            d13al1.casenumber,
            d13al1.type,
            d13al3.workordernumber,
            d13al2.ora_so_header_id_c,
            d13al2.billing_type_c,
            d13al1.id,
            d13al3.id
    ) al14,
    (
        SELECT
            d14al1.id                                       AS case_id,
            decode(d14al2.obq_c, 'true', 'Y', 'N')         AS obq_c,
            d14al2.obq_type_c                               AS obq_type_c,
            d14al2.obq_notes_c                              AS obq_notes_c,
            d14al2.failure_location_c                       AS failure_location_c,
            MAX(d14al2.createddate)                        AS createddate
        FROM
            sfdc.case                  d14al1,
            sfdc.case_resolution__c    d14al2
        WHERE
                d14al1.id = d14al2.case_c
            AND d14al2.obq_c = 'true'
        GROUP BY
            d14al1.id,
            decode(d14al2.obq_c, 'true', 'Y', 'N'),
            d14al2.obq_type_c,
            d14al2.obq_notes_c,
            d14al2.failure_location_c
    ) al15,
     (
        SELECT
            msi.inventory_item_id,MSI.SEGMENT1 ITEM_NUMBER
        FROM
            apps.mtl_system_items    msi,
            apps.mtl_parameters      mp
        WHERE
                mp.organization_id = msi.organization_id
            AND mp.organization_code = '"&ORG&"'
    ) msiv
WHERE
        al12.case_id = al13.case_id (+)
   AND al12.part_number_c = MSIV.ITEM_NUMBER
    AND al12.wo_id = al14.wo_id (+)
    AND xxsov.line_id (+) = al14.ora_so_line_id_c
    AND al12.case_id = al15.case_id (+)
    AND al12.c_type IN (
        'Advance Replacement',
        'Depot Repair',
        'Field Service Visit',
        'LSM Depot Repair/Calibration',
        'Parts Order',
        'Return Replacement',
        'Upgrade'
    )
    AND xxsov.order_status (+) <> 'CANCELLED'
", CommandTimeout=#duration(0, 0, 10, 0)]),
  #"Renamed columns" = Table.RenameColumns(Source, {{"EXTRACT_DATE", "Extract Date"}, {"INCIDENT_NUMBER", "Incident Number"}, {"OPERATING_UNIT", "Operating Unit"}, {"INCIDENT_TYPE", "Incident Type"}, {"CUSTOMER_NAME", "Customer Name"}, {"INCIDENT_STATUS", "Incident Status"}, {"ESCALATION", "Escalation"}, {"INCIDENT_OWNER", "Incident Owner"}, {"INCIDENT_GROUP_NAME", "Incident Group Name"}, {"ITEM_NUMBER", "Item Number"}, {"ITEM_DESCRIPTION", "Item Description"}, {"TASK_NUMBER", "Task Number"}, {"SERIAL_NUMBER", "Serial Number"}, {"TASK_TYPE", "Task Type"}, {"PROBLEM_CODE", "Problem Code"}, {"TASK_STATUS", "Task Status"}, {"OWNER", "Owner"}, {"ACTUAL_START_DATE", "Actual Start Date"}, {"ACTUAL_END_DATE", "Actual End Date"}, {"INCIDENT_CLOSED_DATE", "Incident Closed Date"}, {"REGIONAL_LOCATION", "Regional Location"}, {"INCIDENT_DATE", "Incident Date"}, {"ENTITLEMENT", "Entitlement"}, {"INCIDENT_REPORTED_DATE", "Incident Reported Date"}, {"PRODUCT_FAMILY", "Product Family"}, {"INSTALL_DATE", "Install Date"}, {"ORDER_STATUS", "Order Status"}, {"HEADER_CREATION_DATE", "Header Creation Date"}, {"OBQ_FLAG", "OBQ Flag"}, {"ORDER_NUMBER", "Order Number"}, {"SYSTEM_SOURCE", "System Source"}, {"OBQ_TYPE", "OBQ Type"}, {"OBQ_NOTES", "OBQ Notes"}, {"INCIDENT_INSTANCE", "Incident Instance"}, {"WAREHOUSE", "ORG"}, {"LOCAL_EXTRACT_DATE", "Local Extract Date"}})
in
  #"Renamed columns";
shared ORG = let
  ORG = "SPG" meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = true, Type = type text]
in
  ORG;
shared Local = let
  Local = "ASIA/Singapore" meta [IsParameterQuery = true, IsParameterQueryRequired = true, Type = type text]
in
  Local;
